    title: "Delhi to Jim Corbett: Safari Guide, 2-Day Itinerary & Cab Fare 2026",
    metaDescription: "Delhi to Jim Corbett cab guide 2026. Tiger safari zones, Dhikala booking tips, 2-day itinerary, accommodation, and cab fares from ₹3,250. Complete travel guide.",
