        "12:00 PM — Khusro Bagh. A Mughal-era garden complex with the tombs of Khusro (Jahangir's eldest son) and his mother. Beautiful carved sandstone mausoleums set in a peaceful walled garden. Often empty of tourists. Entry free. 45 minutes.",
