        "4:00 PM — Gandhi Chowk and St. Francis Church walk. The central square of Dalhousie and the surrounding colonial streets are best explored on foot. St. Francis Church (1894) and St. John's Church (1863) are both open and worth a look inside — Victorian Gothic in the Himalayas.",
