        "11:00 AM — Kalatop Wildlife Sanctuary (6 km from Khajjiar). A 32 sq km sanctuary with black bear, leopard, and the rare Himalayan goral. The forest trail through the sanctuary is open for guided walks (₹50 guide fee at the forest gate). Excellent birdwatching — koklass pheasant, Himalayan woodpecker, and kalij pheasant are common.",
        "1:00 PM — Return to Dalhousie for lunch. Café Dalhousie (near Subhash Chowk) for trout fry and rajma-chawal.",
