        "4:30 PM — Arrive Kaza (3,800 m). Spiti's main town and administrative hub. Check in at Sakya Abode (₹1,500–2,500), Spiti Holiday (₹1,200–1,800), or one of the many homestays (₹800–1,200 including meals — preferred for the community cooking experience).",
        "Evening — Walk Kaza market. Small, functional town with a lively café culture — Himalayan Café for yak cheese momos (₹120) and butter tea (₹60). Rest and acclimatise — no alcohol at altitude.",
