        "5:30 PM — Wildlife Sanctuary viewpoints. The Mount Abu Wildlife Sanctuary surrounding the town has leopard, sloth bear, and sambar deer — a short evening drive through the sanctuary on the Guru Shikhar road sometimes produces sightings.",
        "7:00 PM — Depart for Delhi overnight. Arrive by 7–8 AM.",
